    "description_long": "This is a matte black cup with a rounded body and a single, thick handle. The front features turquoise text reading 'WELCOME TO GLORY SOUND PREP' in a bold, stylized font. On the opposite side, the name 'Jon Bellion' is written in a matching turquoise script. Another side displays a minimalist line drawing of a head with a beanie, also in turquoise and white. The cup appears to be made of ceramic or a similar hard material, with a smooth, non-glossy finish. The interior is hollow and dark, suitable for holding liquids.",
